Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:43.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,Fureta kata no mukumori nagareta kimi no namida wa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:49.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Yoake mae ni umarekawaru tsuyosa ni!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:55.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Tatoe hanarete mo futari wa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:01:03.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Toki wo tomete yobiaeru yo Soko ni ai ga areba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:07.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Quest for love, quest for all truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:10.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Osaerarenai jounetsu ga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:16.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mezashita hikiyoseru, kotae wa itsu mo kimi da kara!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:19.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Quest for love, quest for all truth!
